出現病徵，將被送往麥理浩夫人度假村，接受隔離監測。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其餘2宗個案為一對居於武漢市的夫婦，分別為62歲女病人及63歲男病人，2人過往健康良好。他們於本星期三，乘搭高鐵由武漢來港。</span></strong></span>女病人昨日開始發燒，但無呼吸道感染徵狀，男病人昨日開始咳嗽，今日開始發燒。他們昨日到威爾斯親王醫院急症室求醫，並入院接受隔離治療，現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n他們在潛伏期內，都沒有到醫療機構、濕街市或海鮮市場，亦沒有接觸野生動物或禽鳥、或有肺炎或上呼吸道感染症狀的病人。初步調查顯示，兩人在香港逗留期間，入住馬鞍山銀湖．天峰，同住的女兒前日亦開始發燒，將被送往威爾斯親王醫院接受隔離，家傭沒有出現病徵，將被送往麥理浩夫人度假村接受隔離監測。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504720-20200124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504720-20200124.htm&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=419a3d38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504720-20200124.htm&h=58b4e062\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504720-20200124.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b0661be45be43d14e2dd406ddd89677612598aa9","tid":1840034,"uid":30743,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"醫護仲咁撚傻幫政府執屎？"},{"pid":"3768bdad44292d62d98d3e296adcbe0725897043","tid":1840034,"uid":316048,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高鐵病毒直送<br />\n<br />\n未來可能有其他省份感染者透過高鐵繼續黎香港</span>"},{"pid":"9d68a16c01e7ed16e44494035fb7dccdbc884694","tid":1840034,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec25619ac480ba828c4d9aee10baf2fd5fba713","tid":1840034,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2dca5b8a61eb2cec8a2cb9d6dc2955236bcf19","tid":1840034,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img 